bio:
Left to right <br>
Kevin "Snowball" Cote - Drums;
<br> The Drake - Guitar, Vocals;  
<br> Cal Kenny - Vocals;
<br> Ed Young - Bass, Vocals;
<br>
Band is a blend of alternative pop and dance music with music from the 60's, 70's 80's 90's and 00's. U2, Goo Goo Dolls, Pearl Jam, Van Halen, Neil Diamond to Red Hot Chili Peppers, Green day and Van Morrison.<br>


Contact Eddie at 978 239 8551.

